rständnis der Prozesse im Bauwesen bereit sind neue Wege zu gehen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aArchitectural designxData processing. 4aBIM. 4aEntwurf. 4aWorkflow. 7aARCHITECTURE / Professional Practice.2bisacsh1 aBähre, Boris, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aBähre, Boris, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHemmerling, Marco, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMiriam Carlow, Vanessa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRussell, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2020z9783110704679oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978303561902740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303561913340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035619133423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783035619133.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020